Name: Amidst the Stars
Description: KU-Cass has provided you with numerous clues about that mysterious Resonator—some clues can be found on the surface, while others are scattered across Tethys' Deep...
QuestDesc: KU-Cass has provided you with numerous clues about that mysterious Resonator—some clues can be found on the surface, while others are scattered across Tethys' Deep...

Dialogues.Speaker: Speaker_83
Dialogues.PlotLineKey: A light and dreamy frequency fills your mind.
You're as clear as the day I first met you. That unwavering glow.
I will remain here and fulfill my duties.
Yet I wonder where you could be at this moment.
I am unsure... Is Huanglong still how you imagined it to be?

Dialogues.Speaker: Speaker_83
Dialogues.PlotLineKey: A cold and rational frequency overwhelms your thoughts.
Compiling the codebase based on the current epoch of Solaris.
Estimated time required: Seven hundred sixty-three hours and twenty-one minutes.

Dialogues.Speaker: KU-Cass
Dialogues.PlotLineKey: Well? How did it go? Did a big treasure chest pop up in the end, like, "poof"?

Dialogues.Speaker: KU-Cass
Dialogues.PlotLineKey: How can this be? I always find a treasure like that in the games…

Dialogues.Speaker: KU-Cass
Dialogues.PlotLineKey: Okay, then... *sigh* I can't have you go through all those troubles for nothing.

Dialogues.Speaker: KU-Cass
Dialogues.PlotLineKey: For the end of a quest, there must be treasures, and treasures you shall have! Maybe I need to dig around for more intel about this.

Dialogues.Speaker: KU-Cass
Dialogues.PlotLineKey: I'll make an album out of all the photos you took as well.
